Já nevím.

00:31:18.296 --> 00:31:25.668
Je však velmi chytrý,

00:31:27.140 --> 00:31:29.073
velmi inteligentní,

00:31:29.665 --> 00:31:31.399
velmi bdělý,

00:31:33.070 --> 00:31:38.115
